[CENTER]After being a while here on Nexus I have decided to upload some of my Stuff I have made while doing some experimantations with modding ! This Set will add 4 different Swords 1 Axe and 1 Shield to the World of Skyrim ! I hope you like it. At the Moment I am working on some other Projects and I will add soon some more Stuff here. Hope you like it so far. Handpainted Textures and Details mixed with none Handpainted !
